Description: Handle of Rhodian pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp.
Production date: 124 BC (see N. Badoud, Le temps de Rhodes, 2015, 143.)
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.102, 55. Name, Teisamenos.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.1139)
